title: Swamp Thing, Vol. 5: Earth to Earth
description: Returned from his sojourn to hell, Swamp Thing discovers that his girlfriend Abby is being persecuted for their unnatural relations. When she skips town for Gotham City, he follows and runs afoul of Batman, Lex Luthor, and the Gotham City P.D.Collects issues #51 - #56
author: Alan             Moore
